transformations.description: This source is a custom query using a union. The first portion of the query will use the betterview property stg to inner join with betterview property building stg based on property version id, and result set to left join with betterview property detection stg based on property building id.
transformations.name: src_query

object.customQuery:
select
	distinct p.property_version_id as property_version_id,
	p.property_version_number as property_version_number,
	p.property_street as property_street,
	p.property_city as property_city,
	p.property_state as property_state,
	p.property_zip as property_zip,
	p.external_id as property_risk_id,
	p.order_date as property_order_date_of_betterview_risk_data_pull,
	p.completion_date as property_completion_date_of_ordered_betterview_risk_data_pull,
	p.update_date as property_update_date,
	p.latest_image_capture_date as property_latest_image_capture_date,
	p.overall_visual_score as property_roof_spotlight_index,
	b.property_version_id as building_property_version_id,
	b.property_building_id as building_property_building_id,
	b.building_number as building_number,
	b.property_level as building_property_level,
	b.building_area_sqft as building_area_in_square_feet,
	b.building_visual_score as building_spotlight_index,
	b.building_accumulated_risk_tree_coverage as building_aggregate_tree_score,
	b.building_tree_count as building_number_of_dangerous_trees,
	b.create_date as building_create_date,
	b.update_date as building_update_date,
	d.property_building_id as detection_property_building_id,
	d.property_detection_id as detection_property_detection_id,
	d.create_date as detection_create_date,
	d.update_date as detection_update_date,
	d.detection_name as detection_name,
	d.detection_area_sqft as detection_area_in_square_feet,
	bd.uw_dashboard_betterview_details_row_id as tgt_row_id,
	bd.uw_dashboard_betterview_details_md5_hash_value as tgt_md5_hash_value,
	bd.property_risk_id as tgt_property_risk_id,
	bd.uw_dashboard_betterview_details_row_effective_end_date as tgt_row_effective_end_date
from
	(
	select
		*
	from
		(
		select
			property_version_id,
			external_id,
			order_date,
			completion_date,
			latest_image_capture_date,
			overall_visual_score,
			update_date,
			property_version_number,
			property_street,
			property_city,
			property_state,
			property_zip,
			row_number() over(partition by external_id,
			property_version_id
		order by
			latest_image_capture_date desc nulls last,
			completion_date desc nulls last,
			update_date desc nulls last) as rn
		from
			dbo.betterview_property_stg) 
	where
		rn = 1
		and external_id is not null
		) p
inner join (
	select
		*
	from
		(
		select
			property_level,
			building_number,
			property_version_id,
			property_building_id,
			building_tree_count,
			building_visual_score,
			building_accumulated_risk_tree_coverage,
			building_area_sqft,
			create_date,
			update_date,
			row_number() over (partition by property_level,
			building_number,
			property_version_id
		order by
			create_date desc nulls last) as rn
		from
			dbo.betterview_property_building_stg
		where
			building_number in (0,1) )
	where
		rn = 1 )b on
	p.property_version_id = b.property_version_id
left join (
	select
		*
	from
		(
		select
			distinct property_building_id,
			detection_level,
			detection_name,
			detection_area_sqft,
			create_date,
			property_detection_id,
			update_date,
			row_number() over (partition by property_building_id,
			detection_name
		order by
			create_date desc nulls last) as rn
		from
			dbo.betterview_property_detection_stg
		where
			detection_name = 'Overhang'
			or detection_name = 'Yard Debris' )
	where
		rn = 1 )d on
	b.property_building_id = d.property_building_id
left outer join (
	select
		uw_dashboard_betterview_details_row_id,
		uw_dashboard_betterview_details_md5_hash_value,
		property_risk_id,
		uw_dashboard_betterview_details_row_effective_end_date,
		property_version_id,
		building_number
	from
		dbo.uw_dashboard_betterview_details
	where
		uw_dashboard_betterview_details_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31') bd on
	bd.property_risk_id = p.external_id
	and bd.property_version_id = p.property_version_id
	and bd.building_number = b.building_number;
